The paper discusses Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques for translating natural language questions into SQL queries, which falls under the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also focuses on relational databases and their contents, which falls under the sub-category of Databases (cs.DB). The proposed solutions involve machine learning algorithms, which falls under the sub-category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which falls under the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the accuracy of existing methods and proposes a new method, which falls under the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG).
